      },
      "date": "2013-05-13 18:41:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAlso here are the stats I see after 30 seconds of racer:\n\n # cat /proc/fs/lustre/lmv/lustre-clilmv-ffff880170588000/md_stats \nsnapshot_time             1368470382.868436 secs.usecs\ngetstatus                 1 samples [reqs]\nnull_inode                1655 samples [reqs]\nfind_cbdata               9581 samples [reqs]\nclose                     24551 samples [reqs]\ncreate                    1227 samples [reqs]\nenqueue                   557 samples [reqs]\ngetattr                   806 samples [reqs]\nintent_lock               112397 samples [reqs]\nrename                    294 samples [reqs]\nsetattr                   262 samples [reqs]\nreadpage                  1101 samples [reqs]\nunlink                    482 samples [reqs]\nsetxattr                  27 samples [reqs]\ngetxattr                  474 samples [reqs]\ninit_ea_size              4 samples [reqs]\nget_lustre_md             36126 samples [reqs]\nfree_lustre_md            35864 samples [reqs]\nset_open_replay_data      24552 samples [reqs]\nclear_open_replay_data    24551 samples [reqs]\nset_lock_data             342311 samples [reqs]\nlock_match                321782 samples [reqs]\nintent_getattr_async      261 samples [reqs]\nrevalidate_lock           2482 samples [reqs]\n\nDo we really want to keep all of these counters?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
