      },
      "date": "2013-08-21 16:04:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nThe calls to lprocfs_alloc_md_stats() are surrounded by unchecked calls to other lprocfs functions. These functions should be checked for errors but are all safe in the sense that nothing especially bad happens when they fail. However adding honest error handling to these functions is not straightforward. See LU-3808 and LU-3810.",
